Maintainer: Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://foundrylinux.org
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: foundry-kde-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plasma-workspace
Description: KDE Plasma desktop theme for Foundry Linux
 Desktop theme components for the Foundry Linux distribution.
 Ships the KDE color scheme (FoundryLinux.colors) establishing the
 near-black background, warm-white text, and orange (#ff5b1a) accent
 palette used across all KDE applications and the Plasma shell.
 .
 More theme layers (Plasma Style, Look and Feel, Aurorae window
 decoration, Kvantum application style) will be added to this package
 as they are implemented.
